name: RangeSeekSliderClone
summary: RangeSeekSliderClone provides a customizable range slider like a UISlider.
description:
RangeSeekSliderClone provides a customizable range slider like a UISlider.
This library based on [MuhammadjonTohirov/RangeSeekSliderClone](https://bitbucket.devops.nonprod.empf.local/scm/react/RangeSeekSliderClone.git) (Objective-C) and made with Swift.
